flowchart TD
    S[Tool Call] --> PM{permission_mode}
    PM -->|accept-all| ALLOW1[Allow]
    PM -->|manual| ASK1[Ask User]
    PM -->|auto| TT{Tool Type}
    TT -->|Read/Glob/Grep/Web*/safe Bash| ALLOW2[Allow]
    TT -->|Write/Edit/unsafe Bash| ASK2[Ask User]
    ASK1 --> D{Approved?}
    ASK2 --> D
    D -->|Yes| EX[Execute]
    D -->|No| DENY[Deny]
